Usage: unsetMessageLimit [-help] [<prefix [ID1, ID2, ...]>]

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
<prefix [ID1, ID2, ...]>     # If no prefix, remove the default or
                             # user-specified limit on error and warning
                             # messages. All errors and warnings are output to
                             # log. If has prefix, remove the default or
                             # user-specified limit on error and warning
                             # message with prefix. (string, optional)